trans-unit.source: Represents a continuation token for listing operations.
trans-unit.target: Represents a continuation token for listing operations.

trans-unit.source: A method that may return a partial set of results via a <codeEntityReference>T:Microsoft.WindowsAzure.Storage.Table.TableResultSegment</codeEntityReference> object also returns a continuation token, which can be used in a subsequent call to return the next set of available results.
